# Cloudflare Pages Redirects

# ═══════ Old retro app URLs → new locations ═══════
# These were indexed by search engines when the retro app was at the root.
# Pages that also exist in SvelteKit (/about, /projects, /contact) resolve
# naturally; these redirects cover retro-only pages and trailing-slash variants.
/experience   /projects/retro-portfolio/experience/  301
/experience/  /projects/retro-portfolio/experience/  301
/skills       /projects/retro-portfolio/skills/      301
/skills/      /projects/retro-portfolio/skills/      301

# ═══════ Retro Portfolio — Trailing slash consistency ═══════
/projects/retro-portfolio/about      /projects/retro-portfolio/about/     301
/projects/retro-portfolio/experience /projects/retro-portfolio/experience/ 301
/projects/retro-portfolio/projects   /projects/retro-portfolio/projects/  301
/projects/retro-portfolio/skills     /projects/retro-portfolio/skills/    301
/projects/retro-portfolio/contact    /projects/retro-portfolio/contact/   301
